So don't play badly to your colleagues!
If you already know the day before that you will not make it to the office the next day, or that something could come up, which is why you have to stay at home, you should report it in time so that neither the colleagues nor the boss are unexpectedly confronted with the absence.
Sum, Giggling, Phone Calls
One is just deepened in his work, but is suddenly disturbed by the loud giggoe of the colleagues?
Unintentionally listening to a phone conversation that you better not hear?
