All this can be very disturbing, even if they are not exactly deepened in a task (writing, planning, organizing).
Are the others always to blame?
If a project is not finished on time, you have forgotten to send an important letter or important messages, if you do not look for the guilt of your own forgetfulness with others!
If possible, you should not talk about the chaos in the office or the loud colleagues!
It is best to admit your mistakes, and apologize if others were affected by it!
The question of how to make up for the mistake, or to make up for what has been missed, is all too appropriate!
In the office - a feeling like at home?
Track pants and slippers: Comfortable for home, but has lost nothing in the office!
Not even if you would actually allow your workplace to be so casual!
